reviewText: This Virtual Santa DVD is awesome! I get so many compliments on this.  Already recommended to our friends that want to have Santa at their house.
This is a well produces video.

I saw this in a house in another neighborhood and it was adorable and the kids love it! It is classic, endearing and not at all cheesy like one might think. It is clear and the production value on it makes it easy to see from quite a distance. I ordered it for next year and I can't wait for my little guy to experience it.
Perfect condition the kids are going to love it!
